Quidditas entity framework
==========================


Installation
------------

Use the setup.py to create a bdist or sdist you can install with pip.


Directory layout
----------------

quidditas - Quidditas source file and tests
examples  - Contains small example games using pygame and quidditas


Usage
-----

  from quidditas import Quidditas

  q = Quidditas()


Further information
-------------------

See the quidditas homepage for more help at http://quidditas.googlecode.com/

  
